![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/bded5ec7-4d8b-47c8-ae4f-3afebd3074fd/e351.jpg)

In this episode of _Major Issues_, we dive deep into one of the most controversial and game-changing stories in Green Lantern lore—_Emerald Twilight_! Join us as we unpack Hal Jordan’s descent into darkness, the fall of the Green Lantern Corps, and the rise of a new ring-bearer, Kyle Rayner. We break down the emotional beats, the high stakes, and how this storyline redefined what it means to wield the power of will. Whether you’re a long-time fan or new to the cosmic side of the DC Universe, this is one episode you don’t want to miss!

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

